Package org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.internal.vuforia

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    VuforiaTrackableContainer
    VuforiaTrackableContainer manages the parent/child relationship between certain types of Vuforia trackables, such as VuMark templates and VuMark targets.
    VuforiaTrackableNotify
    VuforiaTrackableNotify is an interface through which VuforiaTrackables are informed as to whether they are currently visible or not.

    VuforiaTrackableImpl
    VuforiaTrackableImpl is our system implementation of VuforiaTrackable
    VuforiaTrackablesImpl
    VuforiaTrackablesImpl provides an implementation of the VuforiaTrackables interface.
